        <li>We may combine aggregate data with the personal information we collect about you</li>
        <li>From time to time, Selectiall may use personal information for new and unanticipated uses not previously disclosed in our Privacy Policy. If our information practices change regarding information previously collected, Selectiall shall make reasonable efforts to provide notice and obtain consent of any such uses as may be required by law.</li></ul>
